attributes.title: I think it’s cursed
attributes.review: While downloading the app, my phone died!!!! When I got it on the charger my phone then had an ugly orange 🟠 tint to it. After finally getting my phone to work again, I noticed a lot of ads popping up in other apps that I’d never seen before. For example, some for Russian tourist agencies, space force recruitment, and oil from Saudi Arabia. Amazon then tried to sell me cages. Like why would I need a cage???? On tik tok I couldn’t see any content besides the conservative hype house. Literally everything was blurred out and just a static sound. How am I supposed to watch dog videos now???? Not to mention, other weird things started happening. A roach flew at my face, rats started coming out of the walls, and the neighbors cat died. All within twenty minutes of downloading the app. I don’t know guys...I think there is something really wrong here. Please send suggestions on how to fix. You know I love my maga fam💫💫
